and the results obtained by using the analytical formulas given in eq 59a, 59b, 60a, and 60b are presented. The values of ef2 and re extracted from 7j and NOE at 15 MHz by using eq 60a and 60b, respectively, are excellent since at this frequency the motions of all the carbons are close to the extreme narrowing limit. The situation is different for the values of #2 and re extracted from
